# Modulo dashboard

Escopo
- Indicadores operacionais e visao resumida do negocio.
- Consumo de dados reais de resumo, tendencia e alertas via backend.

Rotas e entradas
- Stack: `src/modules/dashboard/presentation/stack/dashboard.stack.tsx`.
- Base path: `/dashboard`.
- Pages:
  - `landing`: `presentation/pages/landing/landing.page`.
  - `home`: `presentation/pages/dashboard/dashboard.page`.

Modelos principais (interfaces)
- `DashboardKpiModel`: id, label, value, changePct, format.
- `DashboardSeriesPointModel`: key, label, revenue, profit.
- `DashboardServiceSalesModel`: serviceId, serviceName, count, revenue.
- `DashboardAlertModel`: id, source, priority, title, description, suggestedAction.
- `DashboardQueryModel`: from, to, groupBy (day/week/month).

Services
- `dashboard.service.ts`
  - Orquestra chamadas de:
    - `GET /dashboard/summary`
    - `GET /dashboard/trend`
    - `GET /dashboard/alerts`
  - Resolve `workspaceId` via `companyService`.
- `dashboard-api.ts`
  - Usa `BaseHttpService` + `httpClient`.
  - Envia `x-workspace-id` para endpoints de dashboard.

Guardrails
- Manter contratos dos modelos para evitar quebrar UI.
- Nao voltar para dados mock no fluxo principal.
- Sempre aplicar filtros de periodo (`from`, `to`, `groupBy`) nas chamadas.
